_sText:
A narrow, corridor-style map with loads of custom details. Inspired from Doom 3, it's dark and spooky. Supports a max of 42 players (21 spawns per side) but it's not suggested you play with that many at once.

Due to the ammount of detail there are some FPS drops in a few rooms, but it still runs at an average of 40fps+ on my system (Athlon MP 2600, Radeon 9500pro)
